@startuml
participant User
participant Flask Server
participant Wav2Vec2 Model
participant Google Translate
participant DeepAI API

User -> Flask Server: POST /upload-audio
Flask Server -> Flask Server: Save Audio File
Flask Server -> Wav2Vec2 Model: Process Audio
Wav2Vec2 Model -> Flask Server: Return Transcription
Flask Server -> Google Translate: Translate Text
Google Translate -> Flask Server: Return Translation
Flask Server -> DeepAI API: Generate Image
DeepAI API -> Flask Server: Return Image URL
Flask Server -> User: Return JSON {transcription, image_url}
@enduml
